<del rend="strikethrough">worden ſein / gnedıklıch </del> <expan>gelıh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / an <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ecker <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
